#: welcome-butterfly.sh:28
msgid "Welcome to AnduinOS Butterfly"
msgstr "Bienvenue sur AnduinOS Butterfly"

#: welcome-butterfly.sh:30
msgid "Close"
msgstr "Fermer"

#: welcome-butterfly.sh:31
msgid ""
"This system includes the PPA provided and maintained by kelebek333, which "
"makes the following applications available :"
msgstr ""
"Ce système inclut le PPA fourni et maintenu par kelebek333, qui met à "
"disposition les applications suivantes :"

#: welcome-butterfly.sh:32
msgid "share files over a local network."
msgstr "partager des fichiers sur un réseau local."

#: welcome-butterfly.sh:33
msgid "create a shortcut on the desktop to a website of your choice."
msgstr "créer un raccourci sur le bureau vers un site web de votre choix."

#: welcome-butterfly.sh:34
msgid "IPTV player, to watch television channels."
msgstr "lecteur IPTV, pour regarder des chaînes de télévision."

#: welcome-butterfly.sh:35
msgid "Installing additional applications"
msgstr "Installer des applications supplémentaires"

#: welcome-butterfly.sh:36
msgid "You can install additional applications from"
msgstr "Vous pouvez installer des applications supplémentaires depuis"

#: welcome-butterfly.sh:36
msgid "or from the"
msgstr "ou depuis la"

#: welcome-butterfly.sh:36
msgid "Software Center"
msgstr "Logithèque"

#: welcome-butterfly.sh:37
msgid "Playing commercial DVDs"
msgstr "Lecture des DVD du commerce"

#: welcome-butterfly.sh:38
msgid ""
"Commercial DVDs are often encrypted with DRM (Digital Rights Management). To "
"enable their playback, click the three stacked rectangles icon of the panel, "
"then search for"
msgstr ""
"Les DVD du commerce sont souvent chiffrés avec des DRM (Digital Rights Management). "
"Pour activer leur lecture, cliquez sur l'icône des trois rectangles empilés du panneau, "
"puis recherchez"

#: welcome-butterfly.sh:38
msgid "Install DVD Support"
msgstr "Installer le support DVD"

#: welcome-butterfly.sh:44
msgid "Do you want to show this message at startup?"
msgstr "Voulez-vous que ce message s'affiche au démarrage ?"

#: welcome-butterfly.sh:45
msgid "No, don't show again"
msgstr "Non, ne plus afficher"

#: welcome-butterfly.sh:46
msgid "Show again next time"
msgstr "Afficher à nouveau la prochaine fois"
